Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.55,0:01:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#27 日比谷、琴子 談論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.42,0:02:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的，日子過的真快\N在那之後已經過了兩個春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.00,0:02:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是本須和放榜的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.94,0:02:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你開始製作人型  電腦至今\N也已經過很長的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.21,0:02:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛爾塔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，ちぃ她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.45,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了“只屬於我的人”\N過得很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.32,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是段漫長的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.39,0:02:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我換好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然很合身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.17,0:02:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這原本就是妳的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的衣服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳全都忘了，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.11,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ忘了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.58,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是那個人的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（漸漸的         沒有任何人的小鎮）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本書的續集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐，管理員小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉這麼晚還打電話過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問是本須和公館嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田店長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是本須和吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.39,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好我也要找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.66,0:03:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天她沒來店裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心她\N所以打電話問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.57,0:03:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她沒去你那邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再打給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒見過的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是秀樹的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.55,0:04:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳被綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然是那台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小島良由起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺先生打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔打來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次寄圖片來的帳號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛又寄來一封郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經寄到絲茉茉那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打開看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的郵件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟解壓縮檔案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.96,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是送圖片的那傢伙\N綁架ちぃ的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道是\Nちぃ受苦的照片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜻蜓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.63,0:05:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才問那是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫蜻蜓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能知道ちぃ在哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.61,0:06:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，讓我看看妳的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.19,0:06:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜻蜓有20台以上的自製機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.53,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那是間能放得下\N超過20台電腦的大房子囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.57,0:06:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是每間房子都很大耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.07,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我記得\N為了避免那些電腦被偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有跟保全公司簽約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在BBS上有寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找貼著保全公司貼紙的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.05,0:06:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.15,0:06:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定妳真的是Chobits系列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.83,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.44,0:07:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.12,0:07:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡可以進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.84,0:07:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ只要一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有只屬於我的人可以碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.33,0:08:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有只屬於我的人可以進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.86,0:08:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉變得好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是ちぃ做的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹最重要的東西是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是“那個”\N還是對“人”而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.26,0:08:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ或許就不必失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.13,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀…樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.69,0:09:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…ちぃ吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ就是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是秀樹替我取的\N所以叫ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.47,0:09:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹來找我\N我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也一起跟去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責通報上榜與否的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還被設計成\N不做沒有意義的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有意義？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.99,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以本須和考前的能力來算\N合格機率為8.6%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看放榜只是浪費時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有跟本須和提過這件事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.81,0:10:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，因為我被設計成\N只講實話而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.71,0:10:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也跟ちぃ說過\N她跟去也只是白費時間而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.18,0:10:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他們之間的相處模式啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.49,0:10:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模式？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.95,0:10:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦與人之間的關係\N有許多不同的相處模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有很多種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是恭喜你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.27,0:10:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不，還沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.91,0:10:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，那先這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.55,0:10:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說新保找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.59,0:10:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，他也考上不少所大學耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.09,0:10:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不過這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他就快結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得多做點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給新保跟國分寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.57,0:11:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且ちぃ打工店裡的人也說要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要到這裡來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.45,0:11:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，為了慶祝本須和上榜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果落榜的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.35,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有沒有考上\N大家應該都會來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰寄來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情形還不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.64,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.67,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在搜尋連線資料後\N大概有個譜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦的資料庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是柚姬之前入侵的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.11,0:11:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料？\N那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.55,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.75,0:11:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的電腦裡暗藏著\N某些很不得了的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.12,0:11:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連電腦界的帝王\N都想知道的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，ちぃ她真的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不能確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.16,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她應該是Chobits\N或是類似的特殊電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我還不確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.62,0:12:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，該說是掛念好呢\N還是擔心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.66,0:12:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不起的\N並非迷上電腦的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.49,0:12:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是抱著隨便的態度\N跟人或電腦交往的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有哪裡痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.48,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.62,0:13:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你為什麼要抱ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.29,0:13:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.89,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將愛爾塔初始化後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望她能找到\N只屬於她的重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.63,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ對他們而言…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，對現在的電腦使用者而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.94,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是非常危險的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定權在本須和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.48,0:14:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是只屬於我的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ喜歡秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.79,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹喜歡ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.66,0:14:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非做不可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.86,0:15:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與另一個我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.49,0:15:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.27,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ最重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.15,0:15:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ心中最特別的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.25,0:16:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？Chobits？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.56,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼聲紋比對完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，您有什麼命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.74,0:16:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刪除資料，及停止系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ別做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.88,0:16:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.75,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定要刪除資料\N及停止系統嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作業結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.16,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那組密碼只會對\N我與我丈夫的聲紋產生反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.45,0:17:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不了解ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此讓ちぃ感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.49,0:18:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有好好的教導ちぃ\N什麼才是“幸福”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.86,0:18:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果ちぃ還在某處的話\N能幫我轉告她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.17,0:18:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的“幸福”就是\N能與喜歡的人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.17,0:18:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起\N雖然會有許多痛苦與悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.94,0:18:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過若無法在一起\N將會是更痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.45,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓ちぃ得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.17,0:18:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有過一段悲傷的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.24,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今胸口仍會感到悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常悲傷的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明失去了重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.42,0:19:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的痛苦卻仍殘留著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是繼續的尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是我，所以他喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.97,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是更加痛苦的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.21,0:19:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在他身旁只會感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.59,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到痛苦的他\N自己也會感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.52,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定從他面前消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡他所以我消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但看不到他反而更加痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.27,0:20:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到他將會更加更加痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.78,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是因為喜歡他而分開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明喜歡他\N卻要跟他分開嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那會讓他得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福…那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是妳所謂的幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的幸福就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的幸福只能從他身上找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.93,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算感到心痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.94,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，我還是只要他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.45,0:21:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.69,0:21:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過得很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.85,0:22:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.43,0:22:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.67,0:22:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.04,0:22:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒         感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.75,0:22:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.35,0:23:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.72,0:23:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.30,0:23:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.50,0:23:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.84,0:23:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
